Product       : SmolLM2-135M-Instruct (Quantized GGUF version)
Original Model: Developed by Hugging Face (https://huggingface.co/HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM2-135M-Instruct)
Quantization  : Performed by https://huggingface.co/bartowski using llama.cpp.
Format        : GGUF (Method: Q4_K_M)
Download      : https://huggingface.co/bartowski/SmolLM2-135M-Instruct-GGUF/blob/main/SmolLM2-135M-Instruct-Q4_K_M.gguf
Note          : Model file is present only in GitHub Releases due to its size

